sentences.english: Freud and Skinner had explanations of all of these.
sentences.chinese: 弗洛伊德和斯金纳的理论解释了上述一切。

sentences.english: Now, according to Freud, most of this is unconscious.
sentences.chinese: 根据弗洛伊德的理论，人格结构的大部分是无意识的。

sentences.english: How the character of the people get? Freudian said that the character is relate to the experience.
sentences.chinese: 弗洛伊德说，人的性格和人的经历有关。

sentences.english: The work of Freud , Jung , Adler  to some extent.
sentences.chinese: 创建者包括弗洛伊德，荣格以及阿德勒。

sentences.english: We should look on Freud's subconsciousness theory dialectically.
sentences.chinese: 对弗洛伊德潜意识理论必须加以辩证的看待。

sentences.english: Freud was a good student, and very ambitious.
sentences.chinese: 弗洛伊德是一位雄心勃勃的优秀学生。

sentences.english: And dreams had--and this is an idea that long predated Freud.
sentences.chinese: 在弗洛伊德之前就有观点指出。

sentences.english: Eg: Freud is the father of psychoanalysis.
sentences.chinese: 弗洛伊德是心理学的创始者。

sentences.english: On the one hand, Freud made his start as a neuroscientist.
sentences.chinese: 一方面，弗洛伊德在一开始时是一位神经学家。

sentences.english: Sigmund Freud and Henri Bergson are two great philosophers.
sentences.chinese: 弗洛伊德和伯格森是两位伟大的哲学家。

sentences.english: He wrote a letter saying, "Don't give the prize to Freud.
sentences.chinese: 爱因斯坦在信中写到，“请别把奖项颁发给弗洛伊德。

sentences.english: Sigmund Freud also states that we all are born with this element.
sentences.chinese: 西格蒙德弗洛伊德也我们都与此元素出生国。

sentences.english: Freud had made significant revision of its original definition in the later stage of his study.
sentences.chinese: 弗洛伊德后期曾对其原始定义作了较大修正。

sentences.english: And remember the discussion we had with regard to Freud.
sentences.chinese: 回想一下我们队弗洛伊德的讨论。

sentences.english: And this is one of the main critiques of Freud.
sentences.chinese: 这也是大家对弗洛伊德的主要批评之一。

sentences.english: That is the Freudian slip that I've been talking about.
sentences.chinese: 这就是弗洛伊德式的口误。
